name: Ex2: Testing user data on Profile Screen afther chenging on Edit Profile screen

steps.name: User open "Edit Profile" screen on PROFILE screen
Change app age. Click and delete default info. Set new app age as
Change gender first on Other then chose Female
Press save changes button on profile edit screen
Press "Activyty" tub to open activity screen
Press "Earth" tub to open safety screen
Press "Shoes" tub to open shoes screen
Check if user weight: '56', height: '169', age: '53' was changed on settings screen
